body:
### Welcome to My GitHub Page.
I am now learning Swift language, and have updated several projects I designed in my spare time. Though those projects is simple, it can be helpful to someone who is new to Swift. Because they are designed with Swift 2.0 in Xcode 7 which is newer compared to those reference program online. I hope these will help you in learning Swift.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
